01:24:49,830 --> 01:24:51,499
You can stop, son.

1307
01:24:56,462 --> 01:24:58,339
You can stop now.
It's over.

1308
01:24:58,381 --> 01:24:59,673
Hey.

1309
01:24:59,715 --> 01:25:03,969
We'll take it, we can take it
from here. We can take it from...

