1323
01:26:08,074 --> 01:26:10,909
Fuck you and the horse
you rode in on.

1324
01:26:15,289 --> 01:26:16,832
Room 18.

1325
01:26:25,174 --> 01:26:28,302
I want to talk to somebody
in charge, right now!

1326
01:26:28,385 --> 01:26:29,636
Please.

1327
01:26:29,720 --> 01:26:31,722
Who is in charge here?

1328
01:26:33,932 --> 01:26:35,100
Open.

1329
01:26:35,684 --> 01:26:36,977
I'm the head doctor on duty.

1330
01:26:37,061 --> 01:26:39,313
You're the doctor who
locked up Christine Collins?

1331
01:26:39,396 --> 01:26:40,522
Oh, I'm sorry, sir.

1332
01:26:40,606 --> 01:26:42,107
