anyone other than family.

1333
01:26:42,191 --> 01:26:44,777
Oh, you'll damn well
discuss this one. Read it.

1334
01:26:44,860 --> 01:26:45,903
Sir.

1335
01:26:45,944 --> 01:26:47,196
Read it.

1336
01:26:53,035 --> 01:26:54,078
